+# Phase 0284-r1-r2-r1 — Autodoc / Projects boundary rule alignment
+
+## Outcome
+
+The historical 0272 rule now accepts the external ProjectV2 connector boundary
+introduced by 0284-r1-r2 while retaining its former assertions as a fallback for
+an unapplied legacy checkout.
+
+## Scope
+
+- no runtime change;
+- no Scheduler or EventBus change;
+- no SQL, OpenVINO or Qdrant change;
+- no GitHub mutation;
+- no Projects view-management logic added to Autodoc.
+
+## Application context
+
+This corrective patch is designed for the dirty worktree left after
+`0284-r1-r2-autodoc-projects-boundary-realignment` reached the rule gate but was
+not committed.
+
+## Boundary
+
+`newicody/projects` owns active project workflows, forms and views. Autodoc owns
+only explicit connectors, reusable helpers and the copy-source bundle under
+`templates/github/projects-repository/`.
